title: Doctor On Demand® Telehealth: 24-Hour Online Doctor
text: See if we take your plan in just a few seconds: Convenient telehealth appointments for urgent care and mental health support We accept most insurance, which means your visit could be free. *Primary Care is available for select health plans and employers. **People who have a digital otoscope that allows the healthcare provider to see in the ear remotely can be evaluated during a telemedicine visit for ear infections. We partner with leading health plans to serve millions of members around the country. Your telehealth visit may be as low as $0/visit. See if we take your plan in just a few seconds: - Select Insurance Plan - Angle Health - Blue Cross and Blue Shield of Minnesota - Blue Cross and Blue Shield of Texas - CDPHP - Compass Rose - Evry Health - Florida Health Care Plan - Harvard Pilgrim Health Care - Health Plans Inc - healthEZ - Humana Healthy Ohio - Mountain Health CO-OP - Optum - Regence BlueCrossBlueShield of Idaho - Regence BlueCrossBlueShield of Oregon - Regence BlueCrossBlueShield of Utah - Regence BlueShield - SCAN Health Plan - Surest - TRICARE East - TRICARE West - UHC - UMR - Wellmark BlueCrossBlueShield Don't see your insurance listed? No problem. Eligible members may receive $0 virtual care through their employer. Prefer to cash-pay? See pricing below. Create a free account to check eligibility. Limited-time cold & flu offer: Save $15 on cash-pay urgent care visits during the nationwide cold & flu surge.
